00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:47.910
He's also a very
close friend of mine

00:00:47.910 --> 00:00:50.480
and an all-around amazing guy.

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:52.470
So just please give a
warm welcome to Professor

00:00:52.470 --> 00:00:53.094
John Bochanski.

00:00:54.076 --> 00:00:55.465
JOHN BOCHANKSI: Thank you.

