Thank you, Justin.

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:01.500
And thanks to all of
you for coming out

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:05.489
to listen a little bit about
some of the surveys that

00:01:05.489 --> 00:01:08.350
are really shaping the
